================================================================================
TRAE SOLO APPLICATION — ADDITIONAL NOTICE (NOT PART OF THE MIT LICENSE)
================================================================================

This repository DOES NOT distribute TRAE SOLO application binaries, source code,
or assets. TRAE SOLO is proprietary software owned by SPRING (SG) PTE. LTD.
All rights reserved.

To produce the unofficial Linux packages distributed as Releases of this
repository, the build pipeline obtains the official macOS .dmg from TRAE's
own distribution channels (downloaded by the user, or fetched from official
URLs at build time). The build pipeline performs a host-swap conversion so
the cross-platform Electron payload runs on Linux; no TRAE SOLO source code
is modified or redistributed beyond what is contained in the user's own
copy of the macOS DMG.

The MIT license above applies only to the wrapper scripts, templates, build
tooling, documentation, and Linux compatibility glue in this repository.
It does not grant any rights to TRAE SOLO application code, binaries, or
trademarks.

" TRAE " and " TRAE SOLO " are trademarks of SPRING (SG) PTE. LTD.,
used here for identification only.
